PropertySetDef.Name: Pset_SymmetricPairCable
PropertySetDef.Definition: Properties applicable to a symmetric pair cable, which is is a copper cable with a variable number of copper twisted symmetric pair conductors used to transmit data by means of electrical signals. this property set is applicable to type or occurence of _IfcCableSegment_ with predefined type CABLESEGMENT

PropertyDef.Name: NumberOfTwistedPairs
PropertyDef.Definition: Total number of twisted wire pairs in copper pair cables.

PropertyDef.Name: NumberOfUntwistedPairs
PropertyDef.Definition: Total number of untwisted wire pairs in the copper pair cable.
